The MBO and Municipal Accountant to observe the correct and proper use of accounts relative to the nature of expenditures from budget preparation to recording of expenses in order to reflect the true representation of financial position and performance of the Municipality in its Budgetary Reports and Financial Statements, and to submit registries of appropriations to support the recorded budget and actual expenditures under OMOE;
